{
  "stem": "21582.5",
  "chunk_idx": 3,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 4.6,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 3,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 18,
      "text": "And-- and he-- and he was telling us about-- we were just-- you know, the heroic things, how they got the ammunition.",
      "word_count": 22
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 3,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 19,
      "text": "And he was just so-- so committed.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 3,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 20,
      "text": "Then there was another person, a young boy, his name was Benio Posner, and he was a very close friend of ours.",
      "word_count": 22
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 3,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 21,
      "text": "His whole family vanished.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 3,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 22,
      "text": "But then one day-- you know, the-- the partisans moved around.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 3,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 23,
      "text": "They were-- they were like-- like-- they would-- like magic little creatures.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 3,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 24,
      "text": "They would-- you would see them here.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 3,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 25,
      "text": "You'd see them there, and they would disappear.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 3,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 26,
      "text": "And of course there was a great deal of pride and love we felt for them.",
      "word_count": 16
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 3,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 27,
      "text": "We felt like they are-- that they are shining for us.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 3,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 28,
      "text": "And-- he-- Benio came and he told us too that his whole family was gone.",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 3,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 29,
      "text": "And he had some kind of fracture with-- on his-- on his-- either his foot, his ankle, or his toe was either fractured or sprained.",
      "word_count": 25
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 3,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 30,
      "text": "I don't remember.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 3,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 31,
      "text": "But I remember that when he left, we were very, very concerned about him.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 3,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 32,
      "text": "Miraculously, after the war, we found out that he survived and that he-- he-- he went to a friend's.",
      "word_count": 19
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 3,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 33,
      "text": "And he was-- he attended the Sorbonne, and that a professor used some anti-Semitic expression.",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 3,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 34,
      "text": "And he couldn't contain himself.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 3,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 35,
      "text": "He stood up.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 3,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 36,
      "text": "He slapped the professor.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 3,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 37,
      "text": "He said, I can't take it anymore.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 3,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 38,
      "text": "He left friends and went to Israel.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 3,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 39,
      "text": "And he-- he was a pilot and I-- he's still alive, and he's fine.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 4,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Moniek, we never heard from him anymore.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 4,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "That was the end.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 4,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "And now Mr.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 4,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "Szabatnik.",
      "word_count": 1
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 4,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "One day-- now, the-- the-- the bunkers were-- were there, and they were ready.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 4,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "But we did not live in them because we were still working.",
      "word_count": 12
    }
  ],
